'''Dr Ruth Segomotsi Mompati District Municipality''' (e ne e bitswa '''Bophirima District Municipality'''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.demarcation.org.za/Contacts/new_munic_names.aspx| title=New Municipal Names | accessdate=2009-03-08 | publisher=Municipal Demarcation Board}}</ref> pele) ke nngwe ya [[Districts tsa Afrika Borwa|di districts]] tse nne(4) tsa profense ya [[Bokone Bophirima]] mo [[Aferika Borwa|Afrika Borwa]]. Setulo sa karolwana e, se kwa [[Vryburg]]. Karolwana e e na le batho ba ba ka nnang 439 637, mme bontsi ba batho ba ba bua [[Setswana]] (dipalopalo tsa 2011). Nomoro ya karolwana e ke DC39. Ke lona lefelo le le dirang nama ya kgomo e ntsi go gaisa mo Afrika Borwa yotlhe, mme dikgomo tsa mufuta wa Hereford e le tsone di leng kwa pele. Karolwana e e tshwantshangwa le Texas ya kwa USA ka gore le yon ke lefelo legolo la bolemirui. Mmopo le dinawa(Peanuts) le tsona di a lemiwa mo karolwaneng e ya Bokone Bophirima. Leina la karolwana e, ke leina la Meyara wa pele wa Vryburg.

==Lefatshe==
===Mafelo le dimasepala tse di mabapi===
Mompati District e mabapi le mafelo le dimasepala tse di latelang:
* Rephaboliki ya [[Botswana]] go ya bokone
* [[Ngaka Modiri Molema District Municipality]] go ya bokone-botlhaba
* [[Dr Kenneth Kaunda District Municipality]] go ya borwa-botlhaba
* [[Lejweleputswa District Municipality]] (profense ya [[Free State]])go ya borwa-botlhaba
* [[Frances Baard District Municipality]] (profense ya [[Northern Cape]]) go ya borwa
* [[Kgalagadi District Municipality]] (profense ya [[Northern Cape]]) go ya bophirima

